<ul style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;"><li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">God is love is not saying that love is the only attribute of God. It is saying that all of the other attributes of God are motivated by love in addition to His loving character.</li>
<li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">God is just, holy, and righteous and those attributes can result in outcomes that humans would gladly classify as unloving to try and discredit God. But those of us who know God understand that God is always working in love.</li></ul></body></html>